            <fr:title text="scheme">scheme</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  A <html:strong>scheme</html:strong> is a <fr:link href="/forest/algm-000L/" title="locally ringed space" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/algm-000L/" display-uri="algm-000L" type="local">locally ringed space</fr:link> with an open covering on which the space is isomorphic to <fr:link href="/forest/algm-000Q/" title="affine scheme" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/algm-000Q/" display-uri="algm-000Q" type="local">affine schemes</fr:link>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
